last_episode_to_air.name: Girl Trip
last_episode_to_air.overview: A fun road trip ends in murder and mayhem when hidden resentments between best friends surface and everyone learns the hard way to never get in the middle of a catfight.

name: Etheria
overview: From post-apocalyptic westerns to demented comedies to terrifying horror and gore, ETHERIA serves up the perfect blend of mind-bending and panic-inducing excitement from the best emerging women genre directors in the world. Each episode showcases a vision of the fantastic in this new anthology series created to introduce amazing directors to devoted genre fans.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: Featuring apocalyptic westerns, Japanese ghosts, serial killer road trips, parallel universes, angelic avengers, interplanetary kidnapping, last shots at glory, and the worst job interview you've ever had, Etheria Season 1 offers an eclectic array of innovative and shockingly good short horror, science fiction, fantasy, action, and thriller films from women directors.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: Etheria Season 2 shocks and awes viewers with new horror, thriller, and science fiction episodes directed by women featuring killer strippers, time traveling lovers, vengeful girlfriends, vigilantes sex workers and demented wrestlers. Universally praised for their innovative approach to genre, these filmmakers defy expectations and challenge beliefs about women directors.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: Etheria Season 3 takes viewers to strange new worlds with stories directed by women about medieval warlords, magicians, musical androids, apocalyptic western gunslingers, inescapable time loops, dead body buddy comedies, middle-aged female assassins, homicidal hairstylists, demented surreal slashers, spare body parts, and more.

seasons.name: Season 4
seasons.overview: Eight new stories by women directors about time warps, emotional-control apps, unexpectedly upsetting honeymoons, crime lords invading hospital surgeries, burrowing music, A.I. animators, would-be vampire children, demonically-possessed actresses from the golden age of Hollywood, and terrifying Thai dark magic rituals.

seasons.name: Season 5
seasons.overview: Season 5 of Etheria sneaks up on you with savage serial killers, desperate robot husbands, ghostly visitors, gory body horror, demented sibling rivalry, ruinous secrets from the past, witchcraft and witches of several kinds, mermaids, campfire legends, and a hilarious cult indoctrination.

seasons.name: Season 6
seasons.overview: Enjoy adorable werewolves, future dating apps, immigrant experiences, avenging angels, racial tension, bloodthirsty vampires, mutated sea creatures, vigilante mom death squads, the creation of a serial killer, and a girls-only road trip that descends into trickery, madness, and murder.
